         *    ð¼ = 1 + 1/4*((eD^eP + eN^eP)/eD^eP)
         *    ð¼ = 1 + eD^eP/4*(eD^eP + eN^eP)
         *    since eD^eP/4*(eD^eP + eN^eP) is always going to be decimal places in between 0 and 1,
